# DLIIH Rigveda Samhita Frontend Walkthrough

We have successfully developed a premium, responsive, and interactive frontend website for the **Digital Library of Indic Intellectual History (DLIIH)**. The application implements the **Layered Disclosure Model** using Next.js 16 (React 19), Tailwind CSS v4, and TypeScript.

